Borg Says Income Tax Cuts Need to Continue ‘For a Long Time’

-- B y   J a n i n a   P f a l z e r
-- 
2011-10-21T11:21:24Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-21/borg-says-income-tax-cuts-need-to-continue-for-a-long-time-.html
Sweden ’s Finance Minister Anders
Borg said further income tax cuts are necessary to stimulate
growth and need to continue for “a long time.” Borg spoke at
the Moderate Party congress in Orebro today.  Taxes will be lowered only when the economy allows it, he
said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
